data.description: Explore the comfort of this upgraded 2-bedroom,1.5 bathroom condo, nestled in a gated community, offering a secure and peaceful environment perfect for young families. Conveniently situated near a park with amenities like walking trails and picnic areas, as well as the South Coast Botanic Garden, this residence invites you to explore the outdoors.  Step inside to find newly added porcelain floors in the master bath, complemented by marble and quartz countertop vanities, adding a touch of elegance.  This cozy two-level condo offers a retreat from the hustle and bustle, with no neighbors above or below.  Take advantage of the private patio, surrounded by lush California greenery, and enjoy the convenience of upgraded features such as double pane windows and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom's private balcony offers a serene space to start or end your day.  Newly installed HVAC ensures year-round comfort with efficient heating and cooling, adding to the appeal of this inviting home.  Conveniently located near Kaiser Hospital. Job relocation sale, this home is ready for new memories to be made. Don't miss your chance to call this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom space your own. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities!
